{
  "stem": "2718.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the work-- the work I did was any-- any other laborer or any other person who worked in a factory on the-- on the floor level.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't feel-- I didn't feel that that was done unjustly by because why wouldn't I work when everybody else had to work?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As far as I-- as far as my father and my uncles were concerned, they were, of course, doing their work what they always did-- done before.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no different whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that part-- the work part was no-- no problem to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The living conditions were-- were, unfortunately, more of a problem because, as I said before, a family was just four, or-- or two, or 16-- [INAUDIBLE]-- it doesn't matter how many children-- they were all in one room.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, but you have families who were there and a family of seven or eight people, they were still in the one room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody-- every family was allocated one room, regardless And their-- if a house-- a normal house has three rooms, there was three families living in it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was one-- was one kitchen and one bathroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was really a matter of luck whether you were ever in a house with-- with two large families, or three large families, or smaller families.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These were the conditions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and I think we were very happy, even under those conditions, to-- to wait to the end of the war where we were there, instead of being marched off and sent to-- sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, they worked out-- they worked out sort of a common-- common eatery because they had to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The people-- 20, 25 people in a house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There had to be an arrangement.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
